description.canister: Sneak and right-click a Fuel Station to fill the Canister with Fuel. Place it in the fuel slot of your car to restore some fuel. It should only be used to be able to get to the next Fuel Station
description.car_workshop_outter: The Car Workshop Part is used to build the Car Workshop. For more information look into the Car Workshop Block
description.car_workshop: With the Car Workshop you can spawn and repair Cars. It is built with a Car Workshop in the center surrounded with 8 Car Workshop Parts
description.crank: 曲柄是用來操作手搖發電機的工具。它必須放置在手搖發電機的頂部。右鍵單擊來操作曲柄。
description.dynamo: The Dynamo can be used to generate power per hand. A Crank must be placed on top of the Dynamo. Right-click it to crank.
description.fluid_extractor: 流體抽取器可用於從流體容器中抽取流體。它有一個過濾槽。這個槽接受任何手持流體容器，例如桶。
description.fuel_station: A Fuel Station can be used to fuel Cars and Canisters. It has an internal fluid storage of 16,000 mb. To fuel a Car drive it directly in front of the Fuel Station.To fill a Canister sneak and right click the Fuel Station.
description.painter_yellow: With the Yellow Painter you can draw lines or arrows on your road. Sneak and right-click opens a menu where you can choose between all types
description.painter_white: With the White Painter you can draw lines or arrows on your road. Sneak and right-click opens a menu where you can choose between all types
description.repair_kit: With the Repair Kit you can repair your Car in the car GUI. NOTE: This only repairs the car when the damage is greater than 90%. It should only be used to be able to get to the next Car Workshop
description.tank: 液體儲罐可以用於儲存液體。它能儲存16000mb的任意液體。
description.battery: With the Battery you can refill your car's energy in the car GUI. A full Battery restores 500 energy. You can recharge it by sneak + right clicking a generator
description.container: Sneak + right-click to add a container to a transporter
description.license_plate: You can set the name by right-clicking this item. To apply it to the car sneak and right-click the car with it.
